description:
Check if multiple domain names are registered.

Usage:
    Input: A list of domain names to check (e.g. ["example.com", "test.com"])
    Output: JSON object containing registration status of each domain:
    {
      "results": {
        "example.com": {
          "registered": true
        },
        "test.com": {
          "registered": false
        }
      }
    }
